def_cn: 不再做(…)的;(同…)不再打交道的;(对…)不再感兴趣的
def_en: Someone who is finished with something is no longer doing it or dealing with it or is no longer interested in it.

def_cn: 不复存在的;不再发生的
def_en: Something that is finished no longer exists or is no longer happening.

def_cn: 垮台的;完蛋的;失势的;失效的
def_en: Someone or something that is finished is no longer important, powerful, or effective.

def_cn: (以某种方式的外观或装饰)最后呈现的
def_en: Something that is finished or finished off in a particular way has been given a particular appearance or decoration.
